reviewText: This video features some of the most gorgeous models in the world. The models dress sexy, yet in a tasteful way which I appreciate. They do not come off as being slutty. I enjoyed the model interviews, you get to engage with them and see they are real people. My favorite model is Lin Chiling from Taiwan. Her English was very good which is no surprise since she attended university in Canada.

I rented this movie being curious about it. The photography and the movie is cool. If you are thinking that this is a sex video then you might be taken for a ride. It's a modeling video and it has great pictures taken and very awesomely edited video.
